github-restore - GitHub Repository Restore

USAGE:
    github-restore

DESCRIPTION:
    Restore all GitHub repositories to local filesystem using mirror
    clones. Converts repository names back to original path structure.

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-github-restore-path PATH
        Path to restore repositories to (default: /projects)

    -conf-github-git-user USERNAME
        GitHub username

EXAMPLES:
    github-restore
